  "description": {
    "main": "You'll love how good movies and shows look on the Samsung U8000F 50\" TV. The Crystal Processor 4K is hard at work in the background boosting the picture and sound of everything you watch in real-time. Sports, classic movies, and even the nightly news will get an upgrade thanks to 4K Upscaling. And with HDR powered by HDR10+, you'll see more detail, even in extra gloomy or brightly lit scenes.",
    "features": [
      "Samsung Smart TV with a large choice of apps & services.",
      "MetalStream Design for slim, seamless design.",
      "Adaptive Sound adjusts audio based on content."
    ],
    "goodToKnow": [
      "You'll find films, TV shows, and all your favourite catch-up apps on Samsung's Tizen OS.",
      "Play 1000s of Xbox titles and other games on the Samsung Gaming Hub - no downloads, no console, no fuss.",
      "Inspired by aircraft, the MetalStream Design is slim, seamless, and looks great from every angle.",
      "Sound is more realistic with Object Tracking Sound Lite - the TV speakers follow the on-screen action.",
      "Samsung TV Plus gives you instant access to live TV and 1000s shows and movies, for free.",
      "With Adaptive Sound, audio is customised to what you're watching, from whispered dialogue to explosive action."
    ],
    "additionalInformation": [
      "4K Upscaling: Upscaling may not apply to PC connection and Game Mode.",
      "Smart TV powered by Tizen OS: Samsung account required to access our network-based smart services and apps. Subscriptions required. Some apps may not be available at launch. 3rd party content providers may remove apps from the Smart TV platform or stop updating them at any time.",
      "Gaming Hub: Samsung account, internet connection, additional gaming service subscription and compatible controller required. Gaming Hub not available in Republic of Ireland."
    ]
  },
